s-video-for-fan-3498737">Offset announces upcoming LP &#39;Set It Off&#39; and shares video for &#39;Fan&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Thirty Seconds To Mars' Jared Leto recalls unreleased collaboration with Deftones' Chino Moreno https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-jared-leto-recalls-unreleased-collaboration-with-deftones-chino-moreno-3498744?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=thirty-seconds-to-mars-jared-leto-recalls-unreleased-collaboration-with-deftones-chino-morenoLiberty Dunworth Fri, 15 Sep 2023 14:51:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3498744 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jared Leto of Thirty Seconds to Mars performs during Lollapalooza at Grant Park on August 04, 2023 and Chino Moreno of the band Deftones performs live on stage during Rock am Ring at Nuerburgring on June 4, 2022" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> The two recorded the track a decade ago</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-jared-leto-recalls-unreleased-collaboration-with-deftones-chino-moreno-3498744">Thirty Seconds To Mars&#39; Jared Leto recalls unreleased collaboration with Deftones&#39; Chino Moreno</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Jared Leto of Thirty Seconds to Mars performs during Lollapalooza at Grant Park on August 04, 2023 and Chino Moreno of the band Deftones performs live on stage during Rock am Ring at Nuerburgring on June 4, 2022" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto-Chino-Moreno@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jared-leto">Jared Leto</a> of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thirty-seconds-to-mars">Thirty Seconds To Mars</a> has revealed that he recorded a track with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a> &#39; frontman Chino Moreno around 10 years ago.</p><p> The actor and musician shared the revelation in a new interview with Zane Lowe, conducted for Apple Music 1.</p><p> In the discussion, Leto opened up about the inspiration behind the band&#39;s new album <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-announce-new-album-its-the-end-of-the-world-but-its-a-beautiful-day-3440885">&#39;It&#39;s the End of the World But It&#39;s a Beautiful Day&#39;</a> , his tumultuous relationship with drugs and other projects he has pursued outside of Thirty Seconds To Mars.</p><p> It was for the latter that the frontman revealed that he has been sitting on an unreleased collaboration with Deftones&#39; Chino Moreno, from when the two teamed up for a track around a decade ago.</p><p> “I recorded a song with Chino from the Deftones 10 years ago and I never released it,” Leto explained to the host, who soon got excited about the revelation. “I just remembered it. It&#39;s called &#39;Artifact,&#39; which is the same name of the documentary.”</p><p> The documentary Leto referred to is the band&#39;s 2012 film of the same name, directed by Leto, going by the alias Bartholomew Cubbins, which provided fans with a closer look into the workings of the modern music business. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《三十秒上火星》的杰瑞德·莱托：新专辑和兄弟会 |苹果音乐" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A8UczU41xks?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The 2012 documentary also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/30-seconds-to-mars-7-1241945">led to the band being on the receiving end of a $30million (£24.2million) breach of contract lawsuit</a> , filed by EMI over the delivery of albums and royalty disputes. It also led to one of the most popular albums &#39;This Is War&#39;.</p><p> Although Leto kept any specific details on the collaborative track brief and did not specify why the song was later shelved, he did tell the host that he had “a wild time” working with Moreno, and confirmed that he was going to “look for that song [and see] if I can find it”.</p><p> When asked about the sound of the track, the musician responded: “It&#39;s a rock song for sure… I remember he showed up, he&#39;s like, &#39;Yeah, I&#39;m down. Let&#39;s do this.&#39; Which was great because I&#39;m a huge fan of his and Deftones. I mean incredible, incredible band. Great, great, great band.”</p><p> Elsewhere in the interview, Leto also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jared-leto-looks-back-on-being-always-interested-in-drugs-from-a-young-age-3498608">opened up about his relationship with drugs over the years</a> , and admitted that he had been curious about experimenting with different substances since he was young. </p><figure id="attachment_3498615" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3498615" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3498615" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270.jpg" alt="《三十秒上火星》的杰瑞德·莱托于 2023 年 9 月 12 日出席在保德信中心举行的 2023 年 MTV 音乐录影带颁奖典礼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Jared-Leto@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3498615" class="wp-caption-text"> Jared Leto of Thirty Seconds to Mars attends the 2023 MTV Video Music Awards at Prudential Center on September 12, 2023. CREDIT: Jason Kempin/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我是在一个充满毒品的环境中长大的。 I mean, I knew what the smell of weed is, as a very, very young kid,” the 51-year-old recalled to Lowe.</p><p> “我记得小时候走过一些树，比如灌木丛之类的东西，非常小的孩子，也许，我不知道，四年级什么的。 And saying to the other kids, &#39;Oh, someone&#39;s smoking pot there.&#39; They&#39;re like, &#39;What do you mean?什么是锅？他们不知道那种香料是什么。 But for us, it was pretty normal.</p><p> “I never had a &#39;no&#39; for any of that stuff,” he added. “我一直对此很感兴趣。我一直对毒品感兴趣，我一直对体验感兴趣。我一直对冒险感兴趣。”</p><p>在杰瑞德·莱托的其他新闻中，上个月三十秒上火星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-share-rousing-new-single-seasons-3483847">分享了他们的新单曲《Seasons》</a> ——这是他们第六张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-announce-new-album-its-the-end-of-the-world-but-its-a-beautiful-day-3440885">《It&#39;s The End Of The World But It&#39;s A Beautiful Day》</a>中的第四首单曲。</p><p>它是之前单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-thirty-seconds-to-mars-motivational-new-song-get-up-kid-3468719">《Get Up Kid》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-announce-new-album-its-the-end-of-the-world-but-its-a-beautiful-day-3440885">《Stuck》</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hbZYIBy0BWU">《Life Is Beautiful》</a>的后续作品，完整的 LP 于今天（9 月 15 日）发行。</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thirty-seconds-to-mars-jared-leto-recalls-unreleased-collaboration-with-deftones-chino-moreno-3498744">Thirty Seconds To Mars&#39; Jared Leto recalls unreleased collaboration with Deftones&#39; Chino Moreno</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
